{
  "stem": "19921.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the whole family-- what good was with this army is, if the army goes, wherever it goes, at that time everybody knew that they are going to go to Iran and to Palestine because at that particular time, they supposed to have fought before that on Eastern Front but unfortunately, didn't come out because they didn't have enough soldiers.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they decided to wait and go when they, when they have more divisions than just one.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In any event, we didn't know it then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is after the facts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm talking here about the facts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know anything about this secret, what was going on, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In any event, the army was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was organized, and it was moved-- the first segments of it, like 40,000, whatever it is, was moved to Iran.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From Iran it was moved to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And families did follow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And unfortunately, we did not get notification.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Another transport went out, altogether, as we found out later, something like 70,000 soldiers were moved to Iran, Palestine, and then whatever, to Britain and wherever they were sent.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And unfortunately, and the families.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All total as I found out later was something like 140,000 people, with the families.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And among the people was also, as you probably know, was Menachem Begin, one of our future, past, Prime Ministers of Israel.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was, as a matter of fact, in a camp about 80 kilometers away from us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were a couple other people which was together with us on the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They, they moved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They moved.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My professor, which was Professor Landfish, he was able to move also with the army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we found out that there was a quota on the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Simply as that.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
